Detailed Description

cvmx_gmx::_rx::_stats_pkts_dmac

Count of all packets received that were dropped by the dmac filter. Packets that match the DMAC will be dropped and counted here regardless of if they were bad packets. These packets will never be counted in GMX_RX_STATS_PKTS. Some packets that were not able to satisify the DECISION_CNT may not actually be dropped by Octeon, but they will be counted here as if they were dropped.
